channel.title: [SHARD] RealityScape Release - Godwars map [FIRST RELEASE]
channel.description:
MY NAME ON R-S is Reality'! Don't post this anywhere else without my permission!
My first server release, please don't flame because I've done very much to the server and it's a Shard based server.
Hello, this is just my advertisement page, have fun with it. I'm starting new project. Rep is friendly accepted, don't flame on this thread because I've put much effort in it. For noobs.. you can just download and host it. I don't need it anymore, it never crashed and there was never duped on my server! :) So I am releasing this! Download the cache via the client!
Download Server: [url=http://uppit.com/i6mvr3bsx0to/RS_Server.rar]UppIT - Free File Sharing - RS Server.rar[/url] Client: [url=http://uppit.com/s1zxdlglzgla/RS_Client.rar]UppIT - Free File Sharing - RS Client.rar[/url] Cache: http://uppit.com/byktzzrd3vbf/realitysftw.rar
~~~~ [b]Information[/b] ~~~~ You can get castlewars, fight pits and pest control to work, just make the object click work, I couldn't fix it, because it had some weird errors. Maybe you can! Just make the object you join in the minigame work ;)
Custom minigames - Barbarian Assault - Treasure Travel - More coming soon Chaos Elemental King black dragon Dagganoth Kings Kalphite Queen [u]All[/u] specials working [u]All[/u] skills working [u]All[/u] working Knifes Skillcape emotes
